<plot>Very loosely based off Aesop's fable "The Old Man and Death," A Matter of Choice is a film about the decisions that we make that affect our life. Adam is a man with nothing left but his faithful dog, Gritz (Levi). Down on his luck, Adam is now faced with the most important choice of his life. Michael Ray Reed also stars in this short film of choice.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?013034</url></doc>
